Miska Pho - Fullstack Restaurant Management System:

Miska Pho is e-commerce and management solution for a Vietnamese restaurant. 
This project demonstrates full-stack using the MERN (MongoDB, Express, React, Node.js).
Featuring real-time menu management, secure online payments, and a professional administrative dashboard.

System Architecture:

The project is structured as a Monorepo, divided into three main specialized modules:
/frontend: The customer-facing application. Browse dishes, manage a shopping cart, and book tables.
/admin: A secure portal for restaurant owners to manage orders inventory, and reservations.
/backend: The central nervous system. A RESTful API handling authentication, Stripe payments, and database logic.

Live Demo Links:

Customer App https://miska-pho-frontend.vercel.app/

Admin Panel https://miska-pho-admin.vercel.app/

API Server https://miska-pho-backend.vercel.app/

Key Technical Features:

1.Secure Identity Management:
Implemented JWT for stateless authentication.
Role-Based Access Control to separate Customer and Admin privileges.
Secure password hashing using bcryptjs.

2.Online Payment Integration:
Full Stripe supporting credit card transactions.
Webhook-ready logic for payment verification.
Support for both Online Payment and Cash on Delivery.

3.Cloud-Native Media Handling:
Dynamic image management using Cloudinary.
Automated image uploads for menu items via Multer middleware.

4.Real-time Booking Engine:
Custom logic to prevent overlapping table reservations.
Admin confirmation/cancellation workflow.

Tech Stack Summary:

Frontend: React, Tailwind CSS, React Router DOM, Axios.
Backend: Node.js, Express.js.
Database: MongoDB Atlas with Mongoose ODM.
Deployment: Vercel.
